<body>

<div class="navbar">
  <div><b>VeritasESG</b></div>
  <div>
    <a href="/submit">Submit Report</a>
    <a href="/reports">View Reports</a>
    <a href="/verify">Verify</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">
<h1>ESG Reporting Dashboard</h1>
<p>
VeritasESG provides a tamper-evident ESG disclosure system using cryptographic
Merkle commitments. Organizations submit ESG reports which are hashed and
committed to a verifiable audit structure.
</p>

<button onclick="location.href='/submit'">Submit ESG Report</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>System Features</h2>

<ul>
<li>Tamper-evident ESG data storage</li>
<li>Merkle Tree based cryptographic commitments</li>
<li>Auditor verification via Merkle proofs</li>
<li>Blockchain anchoring (future integration)</li>
</ul>

</div>

</div>

</body>
